{"tid":264419,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《藥到命除》固弄玄虛足二個鐘","createTime":"2017-05-30T19:50:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T09:08:51.000Z","uid":59014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f351412b16f93a909306c3f559abf2e33f6ab212","tid":264419,"uid":59014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T19:50:11.000Z","msg":"成套戲拖左140分鐘，去到120分鐘都仲係營造緊問題同氣氛出黎，線索相連性唔緊扣，個感覺好似東一忽西一忽咁併合出黎，完全浪費左前面鋪咁耐既劇情<br />\n<br />\n基本上就係講一個想亂倫既變態醫生研究出長生不老既方法，一直搵水魚落疊去續命既故事。<br />\n<br />\n但無關枝節既場面太多，火足跳舞賴有優雅，又成班痴線既人圍毆男主角，又係沖涼室見到馬定羊，又去酒吧搵無關痛癢既屠夫問話，似癲非癲眾人皆醉唯佢獨醒既男主，無神神淫笑既男主，有理說不清既老女人<br />\n<br />\n就算你格硬解釋比我聽都無用，套戲完全無畫面想表達比觀眾聽有呢個信息，立立雜雜多舊魚既場面太多，完全固弄玄虛，想觀眾估導演同編刻心入面條蟲諗緊乜，無癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b706a90d69bedb7a0529b18a35eeb3799c6efe6","tid":264419,"uid":60733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T23:08:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b91499524f9b3fe856da5259191fa06052da3f9","tid":264419,"uid":54546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T01:55:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">故</span>弄玄虛"},{"pid":"4ae73335c5f33d0a17be01bf260addc012edc38d","tid":264419,"uid":7453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T01:57:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b099d3bf1165ddd38e2bb55772e14223ffb5d44","tid":264419,"uid":3588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T01:58:42.000Z","msg":"套戲隔左咁耐先講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n藥到命除節奏太慢 無解釋太完整"},{"pid":"d7dbc7436cb9608f04cc49b232120f9a7bfdb101","tid":264419,"uid":39576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T02:28:10.000Z","msg":"之前仲成班蓮登仔幫佢腦補<